    <item>
      <title>大型科技公司未能让华尔街相信人工智能会带来回报</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/big-tech-fails-to-convince-wall-street-that-ai-is-paying-off</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚马逊公司、微软公司和 Alphabet 公司在进入本财报季之前都有一项任务：证明他们各自投入到推动人工智能热潮的基础设施上的数十亿美元正在转化为实际销售额。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/big-tech-fails-to-convince-wall-street-that-ai-is-paying-off</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 08:39:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>LG 集团 IT 服务部门有望在韩国上市</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/lg-group-s-it-services-unit-is-said-to-gear-up-for-ipo-in-korea</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，LG 集团的信息技术服务部门正准备最早于 2025 年在首尔进行首次公开​​募股 (IPO)。]]></description>
