    <item>
      <title>苹果撤下泰国广告 遭泰国民众强烈反对并呼吁抵制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/apple-pulls-commercial-after-thai-backlash-calls-for-boycott</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国科技巨头苹果公司撤下了一部在泰国拍摄的广告，因为遭到了立法者、影响力人士和民众的强烈反对，并呼吁抵制这部短片，因为他们认为该东南亚国家的描述具有冒犯性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/apple-pulls-commercial-after-thai-backlash-calls-for-boycott</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 07:23:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>任天堂利润因 Switch 老化需求放缓而暴跌 71%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/nintendo-s-profit-slides-as-consumers-await-new-flagship-console</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于消费者等待推出一款替代 Switch 的旗舰新视频游戏机，因此推迟了购买计划，任天堂公司的营业利润暴跌 71%，降幅超出预期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/nintendo-s-profit-slides-as-consumers-await-new-flagship-console</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 06:36:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>软银和 Naver 将出售日本 Line 应用的股份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/softbank-and-naver-to-sell-down-stake-in-ly-s-1-billion-tender</link>
      <description><![CDATA[A Holdings Corp. 是一家由日本软银公司和韩国 Naver 公司各持股 50% 的控股公司，该公司计划通过 LY Corp. 的 1500 亿日元（10 亿美元）招标出售其所持股份。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/softbank-and-naver-to-sell-down-stake-in-ly-s-1-billion-tender</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 06:33:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苹果第三季度业绩表现不佳，但人工智能功能有望推动业绩增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/apple-sales-top-estimates-after-new-ipads-help-bolster-results</link>
      <description><![CDATA[苹果公司预测，其新的人工智能功能将在未来几个月刺激 iPhone 的升级，帮助该公司摆脱销售放缓的困境，而中国业务的销量下滑尤为严重。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/apple-sales-top-estimates-after-new-ipads-help-bolster-results</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 20:31:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚马逊股价下跌，因支出策略可能令投资者失望</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/amazon-projects-profit-that-misses-estimates-signaling-ai-costs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚马逊公司冒着激怒华尔街的风险，告诉投资者，目前利润将让位于对人工智能的巨额投资。盘前交易中，该公司股价下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/amazon-projects-profit-that-misses-estimates-signaling-ai-costs</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 20:16:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英特尔销售下滑或创 24 年来最大市场份额跌幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/intel-says-revenue-will-fall-short-of-expectations-cuts-jobs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英特尔公司发布了严峻的增长预测并计划裁员 15,000 人，该公司股价由此遭遇 24 年来最大跌幅，这表明该芯片制造商在人工智能时代的竞争能力不足。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/intel-says-revenue-will-fall-short-of-expectations-cuts-jobs</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 20:07:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国曾有机会引领芯片制造技术，但却错过了</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/euv-chipmaking-how-us-lost-control-of-cutting-edge-semiconductor-tech</link>
      <description><![CDATA[这是一次重大的战略失误。美国在发展当今人工智能革命所依赖的半导体技术方面发挥了至关重要的早期作用。然而，现在垄断该工艺的是一家荷兰公司，而主导生产的则是亚洲制造商。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/euv-chipmaking-how-us-lost-control-of-cutting-edge-semiconductor-tech</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 22:06:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
